references: We also analyze the efficiency of our adapter with other existing efficient parameter tuning methods on the BM3 model. The specific model parameter counts and training costs are shown in Table 4. Compared to the overall model training time, our training time increases by only about 15%, indicating that our method is not only effective but also efficient.
